For those who think by making things easier would unbalance the game:<P>Simply you don't just change the mobs.  Take any dungeon, you decrease the mobs toughness, add more of them, decrease the agro radius a bit tweak spawn rates so that an appropriate level group could move to the next spawn in a reasonable period of time.  This is what would give incentive to "do dungeons".<P>And I think Muse has been reading my EQ Forum posts.  I just yesterday refered to that guy from the Princess Bride always saying inconveivable, and likened it to Abashi an balance.<P>Eryl Flynn Level 45 Wood Elf Bard on Prexus
